Package io.swagger.v3.oas.annotations

Annotation Type ExternalDocumentation

  • @Target({METHOD,TYPE,ANNOTATION_TYPE})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Inherited
public @interface ExternalDocumentation
    The annotation may be used at method level or as field of Operation to add a reference to an external resource for extended documentation of an Operation (OpenAPI specification).

    It may also be used to add external documentation to Tag, Header or Schema, or as field of OpenAPIDefinition.

    See Also:
    External Documentation (OpenAPI specification), OpenAPIDefinition
